Here's how to handle each scenario in MSTest:

## 1. Windows-Only Tests

```csharp
// MSTest v3+: Custom condition attribute
[TestMethod]
[SupportedOSPlatform("windows")]
public void Registry_ReadsValue_Successfully()
{
    if (!OperatingSystem.IsWindows())
    {
        Assert.Inconclusive("Test requires Windows.");
        return;
    }

    // ... registry test logic
}
```

Or use `[TestCategory]` + filter:
```csharp
[TestMethod]
[TestCategory("WindowsOnly")]
```
Then run with: `dotnet test --filter "TestCategory!=WindowsOnly"` on non-Windows.

## 2. Skip in CI (Requires Local GPU)

```csharp
[TestMethod]
[TestCategory("RequiresGPU")]
public void Render_ProducesExpectedOutput()
{
    if (Environment.GetEnvironmentVariable("CI") is not null)
    {
        Assert.Inconclusive("Skipped in CI — requires local GPU.");
        return;
    }

    // ... GPU test logic
}
```

In CI, you can also exclude by category:
```bash
dotnet test --filter "TestCategory!=RequiresGPU"
```

## 3. Flaky External API — Retry

```csharp
// MSTest v3+: built-in retry
[TestMethod]
[Retry(3)] // Retries up to 3 times on failure
public void WeatherApi_ReturnsForecast()
{
    var result = _weatherService.GetForecast("Seattle");
    Assert.IsNotNull(result);
}
```

## 4. Cleanup Even on Failure

Use `[TestCleanup]` — it runs **regardless** of test outcome:

```csharp
[TestClass]
public class FileProcessingTests
{
    private string _tempFile = null!;

    [TestInitialize]
    public void Setup()
    {
        _tempFile = Path.GetTempFileName();
    }

    [TestMethod]
    public void Process_WritesToTempFile()
    {
        File.WriteAllText(_tempFile, "test data");
        // ... assertions (even if these throw, cleanup runs)
    }

    [TestCleanup]
    public void Cleanup()
    {
        if (File.Exists(_tempFile))
            File.Delete(_tempFile);
    }
}
```

---

**Summary of key attributes:**

| Scenario | Attribute/Pattern |
|----------|-------------------|
| OS-specific | `Assert.Inconclusive()` + `[TestCategory]` |
| Skip in CI | `[TestCategory("RequiresGPU")]` + filter |
| Flaky/retry | `[Retry(N)]` (MSTest v3+) |
| Guaranteed cleanup | `[TestCleanup]` method |
